## Getting Started

> Full installation and setup documentation is in progress. See [`docs/`](./docs) when available.

### Requirements

- PHP 8.2+
- PostgreSQL 14+
- Composer
- Node.js & NPM
- Redis *(optional but recommended)*

### Basic Setup

```bash
git clone https://github.com/ngo-erp/ngo-erp.git
cd ngo-erp
composer install
npm install && npm run build
cp .env.example .env
php artisan key:generate
php artisan migrate
php artisan db:seed
php artisan serve
```

Full configuration guide coming in `docs/installation.md`.

